00:35:52.530 --> 00:35:54.612
just to share with the
audience, because again,

00:35:54.613 --> 00:35:55.740
what I really want people

00:35:55.740 --> 00:35:59.290
to do is whatever you feel
like your expression is

00:35:59.290 --> 00:36:03.460
or whatever you feel like you can
do in terms of impacting the world

00:36:03.460 --> 00:36:07.490
in terms of your
accessibility message, do it.

00:36:07.490 --> 00:36:11.270
Don't feel like if it's not
standard, don't do it.

00:36:11.270 --> 00:36:13.610
Just act, just do something.

00:36:13.610 --> 00:36:21.400
I know for me, I love to share
people that I find interesting

00:36:21.400 --> 00:36:22.760
with others in the community.

